== Features ==
* colour management over the Postscript language with CRD's and CDA's
* PDF colour management
* convert complex colour documents to flat representations, e.g. Tiff, PNG

== Investigation ==
  gs -sDEVICE=tiff32nc -o MyOutputFile.tiff -f myCMYKCRD.ps FileToProcess.pdf
where myCMYKCRD.ps is to be created with for instance [http://www.littlecms.com/ lcms's] icc2ps tool. It should contain a CRD.

